casebody.data:
STATE of North Carolina
v.
Brundon MOORE No. 163P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2018 Brundon Moore, for Moore, Brundon. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Scott E. Thomas, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 31st of May 2018 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Carteret County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2018."
